29:30.061 --> 29:32.561
And then you, you know,
you try to hunt down

29:32.563 --> 29:34.863
The publicly available
record on these things

29:34.865 --> 29:36.325
And I mean, an incredible
amount of stuff

29:36.333 --> 29:38.073
Is sort of hidden in plain sight

29:38.074 --> 29:40.128
If you dig far enough.

