30:13.264 --> 30:18.061
Which is the idea of working
as independently as possible

30:18.065 --> 30:21.795
From all of the power
factions and centers

30:21.801 --> 30:23.568
On which you're reporting,

30:23.569 --> 30:27.169
And what we've built here, in
terms of our new media outlet,

30:27.172 --> 30:32.309
Is very much, I think, based
on the ethos that he pioneered.

