should be believed,

31:30.091 --> 31:31.791
And he said...
he said to me,

31:31.792 --> 31:33.261
But I would expand that now

31:33.262 --> 31:35.229
To governments, corporations,

31:35.230 --> 31:37.288
You know, it's not just
the... the government.

31:37.296 --> 31:39.896
It's this... that...
anybody in power.

31:39.898 --> 31:41.428
You must start, as a journalist,

31:41.432 --> 31:43.932
With the assumption that
they are lying to you.

