Oh, I wouldn't... I mean,

01:00:16.213 --> 01:00:18.013
I thought we already
went over this,

01:00:18.014 --> 01:00:20.954
But you will not be identified
as a source for anything.

01:00:20.955 --> 01:00:25.587
Your name will not, you know,
appear as, you know,

01:00:25.588 --> 01:00:28.388
Being connected
to these documents

01:00:28.390 --> 01:00:32.226
And certainly no quotes
from anything we talked about.

01:00:32.227 --> 01:00:36.296
One of David corn's major
scoops was the 47% video,

01:00:36.297 --> 01:00:40.327
Where you had presidential
candidate, mitt Romney,

01:00:40.334 --> 01:00:42.934
Do a $50,000-a-plate dinner

01:00:42.936 --> 01:00:47.236
Talking about how 47%
of the us public were moochers.

01:01:00.051 --> 01:01:02.987
When this comes out,
thanks to David corn,

01:01:02.988 --> 01:01:05.888
It changes the momentum
of the 2012 race

01:01:05.890 --> 01:01:07.660
Between Romney and Obama.

01:01:19.267 --> 01:01:22.436
The president of the united
states defeats mitt Romney

01:01:22.437 --> 01:01:24.797
In this... at this
time right now,

01:01:24.806 --> 01:01:26.266
We have made this projection.

01:01:26.274 --> 01:01:29.009
So, the president
wins this battle.

01:01:34.148 --> 01:01:37.148
When the source
with the 47% video

01:01:37.151 --> 01:01:40.186
Is looking to bring
that to the public,

01:01:40.187 --> 01:01:43.887
He didn't take it
to NBC news or CBS news.

01:01:43.890 --> 01:01:46.260
He takes it to David corn
in mother Jones

01:01:46.261 --> 01:01:49.327
