01:02:10.945 --> 01:02:13.905
Indicating Saddam Hussein
has stepped up his efforts

01:02:13.914 --> 01:02:15.648
To obtain nuclear weapons.

01:02:15.649 --> 01:02:18.449
The latest information,
us officials saying

01:02:18.451 --> 01:02:20.451
That over the past 14 months,

01:02:20.453 --> 01:02:24.788
They have seen Saddam Hussein
trying to obtain weapons

01:02:24.789 --> 01:02:28.219
To try and build an atomic bomb.

