The administration was out there

01:02:34.796 --> 01:02:37.226
Starting to beat the
drums for war in Iraq.

01:02:37.231 --> 01:02:41.066
The new york times, anxious
to be ahead of the pack,

01:02:41.067 --> 01:02:43.797
And to get the real scoop

01:02:43.803 --> 01:02:46.137
When they found people with...

01:02:46.138 --> 01:02:48.868
Administration officials
who were presenting evidence

01:02:48.874 --> 01:02:50.774
That wasn't that strong,

01:02:50.775 --> 01:02:52.805
But the new york times
went with the story

01:02:52.810 --> 01:02:55.110
And then dick Cheney
cited that story to say,

01:02:55.112 --> 01:02:56.579
