equipment he needs

01:03:05.519 --> 01:03:08.419
To be able to enrich
uranium to make the bombs.

01:03:08.421 --> 01:03:09.951
Specifically aluminum tubes.

01:03:09.955 --> 01:03:12.155
There's a story in
the new york times this morning.

01:03:12.990 --> 01:03:16.990
The lead up to the war in Iraq.

01:03:16.995 --> 01:03:20.395
The particularly egregious
case is the new york times,

01:03:20.398 --> 01:03:23.566
There's no question
about it, because it...

01:03:23.567 --> 01:03:26.067
It ran stories

01:03:26.069 --> 01:03:29.799
Contrary to the truth.

01:03:29.805 --> 01:03:33.735
It ran stories that the sources

01:03:33.742 --> 01:03:35.709
Had planted information

01:03:35.710 --> 01:03:39.840
That should have been checked
out and the sources were...

01:03:39.846 --> 01:03:41.706
Were questionable to begin with

01:03:41.714 --> 01:03:44.114
In terms of their
own objectives,

01:03:44.116 --> 01:03:46.676
So the times is
a particular case

01:03:46.685 --> 01:03:49.385
Of particularly great failing.

01:03:49.387 --> 01:03:50.987
There's nothing
like experiencing

01:03:50.988 --> 01:03:53.088
The world's finest journalism

01:03:53.090 --> 01:03:54.960
In its original form.

01:03:56.391 --> 01:03:57.961
And I want to
attribute the times,

01:03:57.962 --> 01:03:59.890
I don't want to
talk about, obviously,

01:03:59.895 --> 01:04:01.825
Specific intelligence sources,

01:04:01.830 --> 01:04:05.199
But it's now public,
that in fact,

01:04:05.200 --> 01:04:08.270
He has been seeking to
acquire the kinds of tubes

01:04:08.271 --> 01:04:10.669
That are necessary
to build a centrifuge.

01:04:12.205 --> 01:04:13.995
I remember, particularly,

01:04:14.006 --> 01:04:17.036
Watching Cheney
on meet the press.

01:04:19.208 --> 01:04:21.738
And throwing out this stuff,

01:04:21.744 --> 01:04:24.644
And saying to my wife, saying,

01:04:24.646 --> 01:04:25.946
"this is bullshit.

01:04:25.947 --> 01:04:27.747
There's something
missing here."

01:04:27.748 --> 01:04:31.078
There will always
be some uncertainty

01:04:31.084 --> 01:04:34.154
About how quickly he can
acquire nuclear weapons,

01:04:34.155 --> 01:04:37.523
But we don't want the smoking
gun to be a mushroom cloud.

01:04:38.722 --> 01:04:40.262
Two days, I think it was,

01:04:40.263 --> 01:04:43.387
Before the war was
launched in March 2003.

