An observation by stone

01:31:06.120 --> 01:31:08.618
And what he thought
journalism was all about.

01:31:08.620 --> 01:31:10.587
In his words,
to write the truth,

01:31:10.588 --> 01:31:12.118
To defend the weak
against the strong,

01:31:12.122 --> 01:31:15.262
To fight for justice,
to bring healing perspectives

01:31:15.263 --> 01:31:19.058
To bear on the terrible
hates and fears of mankind

01:31:19.061 --> 01:31:20.991
In the hope of someday
bringing about a world

01:31:20.996 --> 01:31:24.896
In which man will enjoy the
differences of the human garden

01:31:24.899 --> 01:31:27.729
Instead of killing
each other over them.

01:31:27.735 --> 01:31:29.325
If you look
you'll find much more.

